    <p>The Perl Conference 2017 in Washington, DC (teeecchhnniiccallyyy Alexandria, VA) is a high-quality, inexpensive technical conference with its roots in the Perl Mongers user groups. The conference celebrates the Perl programming language and is meant to be accessible to anyone, regardless of experience, yet valuable to even the most skilled of programmers.</p>

